```plantuml
@startuml IBM_kubernetes-storage

actor User
participant "Kubernetes API" as K8sAPI
participant "IBM Cloud Storage" as IBMStorage
participant "Guestbook App" as Guestbook
participant "Helm" as Helm
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

User -> K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
K8sAPI -> IBMStorage: Request storage provisioning
IBMStorage --> K8sAPI: Provisioned storage details
K8sAPI -> Helm: Install MongoDB chart
Helm -> K8sAPI: Create MongoDB deployment
K8sAPI -> IBMStorage: Request persistent volume
IBMStorage --> K8sAPI: Persistent volume created
K8sAPI -> Guestbook: Deploy application
Guestbook -> MongoDB: Connect to database
MongoDB --> Guestbook: Connection established
Guestbook --> K8sAPI: Application running
K8sAPI --> User: Deployment complete

@enduml
```